            "title": "農曆新年前成功榮升業主！上車客擲538萬買屯門時代廣場兩房｜二手樓成交",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Tm1\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"721\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/d.Hbu_zj40I66FnGuvLmug--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/am730_578/77ad77a000ee7f99362145abf41f01d3\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Tm1</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span>農曆新年將至，買家加快入市，中原地產屯門瓏門第一分行首席分區營業經理梁健文表示，屯門區本月已錄得逾</span>60<span>宗二手買賣成交。其中分行促成時代廣場</span>A<span>座中層</span>5<span>室成交，單位實用面積約</span>487<span>方呎，兩房間隔。</span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span>梁健文稱，單位原開價</span>550<span>萬元放售，經議價後以</span>538<span>萬元沽出，呎價約</span>11,047<span>元。買家為上車客，鍾情屋苑交通及起居方便，上址內櫳企理，見業主願意減價，迅速拍板入市，成功於農曆新年前榮升業主。</span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span>據悉，原業主於</span>1988<span>年以</span>40.66<span>萬元買入單位，持貨約</span>38<span>年，現轉售帳面獲利</span>497.34<span>萬元，物業期內大幅升值約</span>12.2<span>倍。資料顯示，時代廣場位於屯門市中心屯合街</span>2<span>號，</span>1988<span>年入伙，共有</span>5<span>座，提供</span>1,240<span>個單位。</span></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><h3 class=\"mb-module-gap text-px20 font-bold lg:text-px18 text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:即睇屯門時代廣場放盤 (House730);elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://tinyurl.com/4d66w3uz\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span><strong>即睇屯門時代廣場放盤</strong></span><strong> (House730)</strong></a></h3><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 AM730 <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.am730.com.hk/地產/1011160/農曆新年前成功榮升業主-上車客擲538萬買屯門時代廣場兩房-二手樓成交?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/地產/1011160/農曆新年前成功榮升業主-上車客擲538萬買屯門時代廣場兩房-二手樓成交?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/地產/1011160/農曆新年前成功榮升業主-上車客擲538萬買屯門時代廣場兩房-二手樓成交?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral</a></p></div>",
